[{"title":"","body":"Great packaging and mug was nice too :) worth the price!","rating":"5","review_date":"4/13/2019 14:08","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Joelle Zboncak","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"gift-for-yaya-the-worlds-best-yaya-mug","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"تغليف رائع، والكوب جميل أيضاً :) يستحق سعره!","body_zh_TW":"包裝很棒，馬克杯也很漂亮 :) 物有所值！","body_cs":"Skvělé balení a hrnek byl taky hezký :) stál za tu cenu!","body_da":"Fantastisk emballage, og kruset var også fint :) prisen værd!","body_nl":"De verpakking was prima en de mok was ook mooi :) Het geld zeker waard!","body_fi":"Hieno pakkaus ja mukikin oli kiva :) hintansa väärti!","body_fr":"L'emballage était super et la tasse était très jolie aussi :) Ça valait le prix !","body_de":"Tolle Verpackung und der Becher war auch schön :) Der Preis hat sich gelohnt!","body_el":"Υπέροχη συσκευασία και η κούπα ήταν επίσης ωραία :) άξιζε τα λεφτά της!","body_he":"אריזה נהדרת וגם הספל היה נחמד :) שווה את המחיר!","body_it":"Ottima confezione e anche la tazza era carina :) Ne è valsa la pena!","body_ja":"パッケージも素晴らしく、マグカップも素敵でした:) 値段に見合う価値があります！","body_ko":"포장도 훌륭하고 머그컵도 예뻤어요 :) 가격 대비 만족스러워요!","body_ms":"Pembungkusan dan mug yang hebat juga cantik :) harganya berbaloi!","body_no":"Flott innpakning, og kruset var også fint :) verdt prisen!","body_pl":"Świetne opakowanie, a kubek też był ładny :) wart swojej ceny!","body_pt":"A embalagem é ótima e a caneca também é bonita :) Valeu o preço!","body_es":"El empaque era genial y la taza también estaba muy bien :) ¡Vale la pena el precio!","body_sv":"Jättefin förpackning och muggen var också fin :) värd priset!","body_th":"บรรจุภัณฑ์ดีมาก และแก้วก็สวยด้วย :) คุ้มค่ากับราคา!","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"","rating":"5","review_date":"3/31/2019 14:28","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Mariana Emmerich","reviewer